-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/second-death-among-new-york-triathlon-participants-confirmed-by-race-chief.html
A second person has died after being
pulled from the water during the  Hudson River  swim portion of
the New York City Triathlon, race organizer John Korff said in a
telephone interview.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
